Item 5. Other Events.
     On June 11, 2002, American Vanguard Corporation issued the press release attached hereto as Exhibit 99.5. The release announced that Amvac Chemical Corporation, a wholly-owned subsidiary of American Vanguard Corporation, has acquired the Folex cotton defoliant business conducted in the United States by Aventis CropScience USA prior to Bayer AG's acquisition of Aventis CropScience S.A., all as more particularly described in Exhibit 99.5.
Item 7. Exhibits.
