On March 23, 2006, American Vanguard Corporation issued a press release announcing that its Board of Directors has declared a cash dividend of $0.07 per share and a four-for-three stock split of the company's common stock. The full text of that press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and incorporated by reference herein.
 
