Newport Beach, CA  September 14, 2009  American Vanguard Corp. (NYSE:AVD) today announced that its Board of Directors declared a cash dividend of $0.01 per share. The dividend will be distributed on October 9, 2009 to shareholders of record as of September 25, 2009.
Eric Wintemute, President and CEO of American Vanguard, stated, "We are pleased to declare this semi-annual dividend, which continues our tradition of sharing the Company's performance success directly with its shareholders. This dividend payment has been reduced from second half outlays in prior years in response to current challenging business conditions in the agricultural chemical industry. In conjunction with previously announced management actions to manage working capital and reduce operating expenses, the Board of Directors believes that it is prudent for the Company to preserve cash internally at this time."
