2.14 Additional Commitments.
(a) . Provided there exists no Default, upon notice to Agent (who shall promptly notify the Lenders), Borrower may request in writing delivered at any time during the period from the Closing Date until the date that is ninety (90) days prior to the Maturity Date additional term commitments ("") and/or Revolving Commitments from the Lenders of not less than $1,000,000 and in an aggregate amount not to exceed $50,000,000, of which additional Revolving Commitment shall not be more than $20,000,000 in the aggregate. No more than three such requests may be made. At the time of sending such notice, Borrower (in consultation with Agent) shall specify the time period within which each Lender is requested to respond (which shall in no event be less than ten Business Days from the date of delivery of such notice to the Lenders).
